32
00:02:19,630 --> 00:02:21,840
The court will surely
send a new imperial envoy.

33
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:22,800
We must find evidence

34
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,870
before the new imperial envoy

35
00:02:23,870 --> 00:02:24,870
