44
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:42,670
Young Master,

45
00:02:42,790 --> 00:02:43,910
that Kaitai Teahouse

46
00:02:43,910 --> 00:02:45,150
is right by the east gate.

47
00:02:45,150 --> 00:02:46,310
Outside its doors,
there's a constant stream of traffic

48
00:02:46,310 --> 00:02:47,110
day and night.

49
